Kalisha.Naicker THE Hillcrest Homing Pigeon Club is calling on the community to join in this exciting sport. Club members meet between May and September and every Thursday evening there is the basketing night when members meet at the club with their birds to be raced.There are currently 27 members and the Upper Highway community is urged to join.For more information contact ssmarketing@polka.co.za - Supplied.24.com encourages commentary submitted via MyNews24. Contributions of 200 words or more will be considered for publication.